title: Pray at Altar Teleportation
story: dungeo
description: Tests PRAY action at Altar teleports to Forest Path 1 (per Fortran sverbs.for V79)

---

# Setup: Get lamp and go to Altar using GDT
> gdt
[OK: contains "GDT"]

> tk brass lantern
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> ah Altar
[OK: contains "Altar"]

# Turn on lamp so we can see
> turn on lantern
[OK: contains "on"]

# Verify we're at the Altar
> look
[OK: contains "Altar"]
[OK: contains "stone altar"]

# Pray at the Altar - should teleport to Forest
> pray
[OK: contains "prayer"]
[OK: contains "answered"]

# Verify we're now in Forest Path (teleported)
> look
[OK: contains "Forest Path"]
[OK: contains "winding through"]
[OK: contains "tree"]

